data.title: 'SEAL Team Six' Gets Some Of Bin Laden Raid Right
data.meta_description: The National Geographic Channel's movie about the raid that killed Osama bin Laden premieres Sunday night. Weekend Edition host Rachel Martin spoke with NPR's Pentagon correspondent Tom Bowman about how accurate the film is compared to the real story.
